title: Map reading: Benalla, Wangaratta, Tungamah
brief_description: RAAF training film contains aerial views of Benalla, Wangaratta, and Tungamah. Divided by black and white intertitles, the film shows (from the pilot’s perspective), the countryside approaching and leaving Benalla, Wangaratta, and Tungamah.
